    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>«笼罩一切的黑暗»</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在一段感人至深的故事中，这个故事讲述了一场沉重的家庭悲剧。每一步都可能带来出乎意料的结局。每一段找到的日记碎片、每一张留下的便条以及每一道阴沉的声音，都在逐步揭示剧情的全貌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>平均游玩时间：30 分钟</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296370/extras/1bf40d1abe12bca925dff8b5db6ef44c.poster.avif?t=1748015545\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296370/extras/1bf40d1abe12bca925dff8b5db6ef44c.webm?t=1748015545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296370/extras/1bf40d1abe12bca925dff8b5db6ef44c.mp4?t=1748015545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>«Cursed New Year»</strong> 将带您进入一座阴森宅邸的氛围，让您体验丰富而强烈的情感，同时依靠逼真的画面和高品质的音效助您一臂之力。游戏旨在营造持续紧张的氛围，并呈现出色、恰到好处的惊吓效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年轻的莎拉在她清醒的生活中大部分时间都在两位慈爱的父母陪伴下度过，但家庭中发生的悲剧对每个家庭成员的命运都产生了深远影响。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296370/extras/de80c2b3a99c49fd7864b995724b7c86.poster.avif?t=1748015545\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296370/extras/de80c2b3a99c49fd7864b995724b7c86.webm?t=1748015545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296370/extras/de80c2b3a99c49fd7864b995724b7c86.mp4?t=1748015545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-类型：«步行模拟器»；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-游戏画面和氛围达到极致真实；<br>-在游戏过程中，您将听到营造氛围的音效；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-游戏包含一个精心设计的剧情，您可以在游戏过程中进行调查；</p>",
